Thandiwe Rose Marry Zungu (amụrụ n'abalị itoolu n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ n'afọ 1960) bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Africa na onye omeiwu (MP) maka African National Congress si KwaZulu-Natal
A mụrụ Zungu n'ụbọchị nke itoolu n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ n'afọ 1960
O nwere asambodo na njikwa na asambodo na idu ndú site na Mahadum Teknụzụ nke Durban

Onye otu African National Congress, a họpụtara ya dị ka onye na-ahụ maka akụ nke mpaghara Moses Mabhida nke pati ahụ na 1989. N'afọ 2008, a họpụtara ya dị ka onye otu kọmitii ntụziaka mpaghara nke ANC na kọmitii ọrụ mpaghara. Zungu ghọrọ onye otu kọmitii na-ahụ maka mpaghara nke African National Congress Women's League na 2017.
Zungu guzoro dị ka onye omeiwu ANC si KwaZulu-Natal na ntuli aka mba 2019 ma họpụta ya na National Assembly ma ṅụọ iyi na 22 Mee 2019.

N'abalị iri abụọ na asaa n'ọnwa Juun afọ 2019, Zungu ghọrọ onye otu National Assembly's Portfolio Committee on International Relations and Cooperation. A kpọrọ ya aha na Joint Standing Committee on Defence na 5 Septemba 2019.
